title: 152: DJ's Top 50 prospects, incoming QBs, WRs, RBs and more
itunes:title: 152: DJ's Top 50 prospects, incoming QBs, WRs, RBs and more
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are on the road to scout the talent at the East-West Shrine Game. In this episode Daniel Jeremiah reveals his list of the Top 50 prospects. DJ and Bucky also debate the ranking among the top QBs, RBs, WRs and other positions.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
